# Shopify (mitipi-2)

- Store: `mitipi-2.myshopify.com`. Secrets in gitignored `.env` only.
- Token: `SHOPIFY_CLIENT_ID` + `SHOPIFY_CLIENT_SECRET` → `./scripts/shopify-refresh-admin-token.sh` or auto-refresh in `scripts/lib/shopify-admin-gql.mjs`.
- MCP `user-shopify-dev-mcp`: call `learn_shopify_api` first; pass `conversationId` to `search_docs_chunks` / `validate_graphql_codeblocks`.
- Product create needs app scope `write_products` on lurafi Dev Dashboard version.
